            <p class="front-about__text" data-aos="fade-top" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="500">The company Penthouse.ae powered by Metropolitan is distinguished
                by
                extensive work experience in Dubai’s real estate market. Our team comprises the best
                professionals who clearly understand and recognize the market and will be happy to help you
                acquire luxurious real estate in the emirate.</p>

            <div class="front-about__text-2">
                <p data-aos="fade-top" data-aos-duration="600" data-aos-delay="700">High-profile clients of our agency enjoy a privileged access to exclusive luxurious
                    properties across the most prestigious destinations in the emirate, which are not
                    available
                    to the general public. Individual approach to each client, ability of our property
                    specialists to find right buyer to the seller, transparency of all transactions as well
                    as
                    power of our network make Penthouse.ae powered by Metropolitan different from other real
                    estate agencies in Dubai. </p>
